start broken systems, repair walls and engines, and decide which sections of the ship to keep pressurized in order to protect your cargo.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SURVIVE THE HORROR</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1111920/extras/a954a5933fd266d04c1685c049d59d90.poster.avif?t=1745556118\" width=600 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1111920/extras/a954a5933fd266d04c1685c049d59d90.webm?t=1745556118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1111920/extras/a954a5933fd266d04c1685c049d59d90.mp4?t=1745556118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Investigate derelict craft and passing planetoids for trash and treasures. </strong> Beware the dangers lurking within. Spacewalk your way to riches or ruin, and get used to dragging your friend’s corpses back to the respawn platform.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DELIVER THE CARGO</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1111920/extras/07e3d8890af2a0d2f70dc39e0a0d53f2.poster.avif?t=1745556118\" width=600 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1111920/extras/07e3d8890af2a0d2f70dc39e0a0d53f2.webm?t=1745556118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1111920/extras/07e3d8890af2a0d2f70dc39e0a0d53f2.mp4?t=1745556118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unload cargo onto the cargo platform while still warding off possi